  ],
  "remarks": "JSC “Ulyanovsk Mechanical Plant” is a Russian diversified enterprise, manufacturing short-range and medium-range air defence systems and radar systems. It is a subsidiary of JSC Concern VKO Almaz-Antey, part of the military-industrial complex of Russia. JSC Ulyanovsk Mechanical Plant provides anti-aircraft missile systems and radar systems that the Russian Armed Forces are using in the war of aggression against Ukraine. Therefore, JSC Ulyanovsk Mechanical Plant is supporting materially actions which undermine and threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}